  "title": "Front Desk Customer Service Officer (Aesthetic Clinic) #81949",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Medical Aesthetic/ Skincare</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Front Desk Customer Service Officer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Orchard/ Novena (near MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 Days, Mon – Fri (10am – 8pm), Sat (10am – 5pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Handle incoming calls and enquiries, provide accurate information to patients in a friendly and professional manner.</li><li>Manage patient registration, update personal details, and maintain proper filing/ records.</li><li>Scheduling of patient appointments.</li><li>Perform cashiering duties, process payments, and issue receipts accurately.</li><li>Support dispensary operations by preparing/ dispensing clinic products and medications.</li><li>Maintain inventory by sorting, counting, replenishing stock, and ensuring the dispensary area remains clean and organized.</li><li>Assist with purchase orders and delivery orders, including receiving items and supporting stock take activities.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE O-Level.</li><li>Prior experience in a clinic, receptionist, cashier, or similar customer-facing role preferred.</li><li>Good interpersonal and communication skills.</li><li>Able to multitask, work independently and as part of a team, and perform well in a fast-paced environment.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81949 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
